.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/KcEYGHN</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[NationalOrganizationOfMenAgainstAmazonianMasterhood]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>For my 37th birthday I decided to start taking care of myself. Six months progress</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/0TxLYBU</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ECcmi85.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I got a desk job seven years ago and slowly started putting on weight due to some depression, drinking too much and lack of exercise.  I decided to get serious about my health around the first week of December. I haven’t been perfect but I think I’ve done pretty well. I’ve always had some self image problems but I felt pretty good today.  #progress_pic #progress</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0TxLYBU</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ChrisE13579]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I know selfies are forbidden but I want to celebrate being elected as a Town Councillor.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/qk3ymI5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yrDMCVt.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/qk3ymI5</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheMasterandMargarita]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cancer spread to the brain</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WsldJv1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/a7IuEPo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Had radiation on my brain yesterday. Imgur you were such a huge support when I started this journey as stage III just reaching out to give an update and ask for good vibes ? I have one tumor in my brain that Mayo radiated yesterday and I start targeted infusions this Tuesday. I’ll take these every 3 weeks and in 2 months they will do a new brain MRI at that time. They said I have a chance of them doing this and it never coming back or if it does years from now the targeted drug slows it down to. Also, could go quickly too if it doesn’t respond to therapy so really planning both scenarios. Would love any good vibes or send funny memes!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WsldJv1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Amber35]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Lizard Loves Mango</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PTx1BkB</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8qsfb0I.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PTx1BkB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ElbowDeepInACentaur]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>And he designs brilliant cars</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/u03Q45q</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CysWofL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/71tCJ6k.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/u03Q45q</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PC54]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sunday PACs</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VVFLlF3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hGrgJUJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>With music and little sandwiches</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VVFLlF3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DanCTheman]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Well, yeah true?</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/BIIMD4m</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/J1LuCYf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/BIIMD4m</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PhoneRepairTech]]></dc